1
00:01:21,420 --> 00:01:26,850
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,570 --> 00:01:29,710
[Episode 31]

3
00:01:30,430 --> 00:01:31,960
You are slandering me!

4
00:01:32,789 --> 00:01:33,509
Master!

5
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:34,650
Drag him out.

6
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:35,650
Yes, sir.

7
00:01:35,710 --> 00:01:36,280
You...

8
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,870
I will report this to His Majesty!

9
00:01:38,870 --> 00:01:39,280
Move.

10
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:41,140
I will report this to His Majesty!

11
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:46,250
[Xianke Pavilion]

12
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:41,789
Hurry up.

13
00:01:41,789 --> 00:01:42,640
Let go of me!

14
00:01:46,380 --> 00:01:49,030
[Identity Verified: An Deyu, Investigating Censor of the Censorate]

15
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,039
To the next house.

16
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:51,509
My Lord,

17
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,310
we've arrested quite a few today.

18
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:54,840
Do you want to

19
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,150
go back and rest for a bit?

20
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,009
No time to rest.

21
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,880
This bird's nest is excellent.

22
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:13,590
Have you heard

23
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,280
about Ye Xian?

24
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:16,750
Yes, I have.

25
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,360
His Majesty has transferred

26
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,630
all cases related to the Inner Court

27
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:21,120
to the Xuanfeng Guard.

28
00:02:21,270 --> 00:02:23,590
They've arrested
several imperial censors in a row,

29
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:24,310
all of whom had previously

30
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:26,240
impeached the Marquis Changxing.

31
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,960
I also heard

32
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:30,150
he was always frail.

33
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,630
Just climbing a mountain

34
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:32,310
would cost him

35
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,590
half his life.

36
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,280
How is it that when handling cases,

37
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,430
he is so ruthless?

38
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,280
Isn't it because

39
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,710
his beloved one

40
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,310
was taken away from him?

41
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,130
Speaking of which, I'm quite curious.

42
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:47,590
Although Madam Chen isn't
from a noble family,

43
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,910
the Gu family

44
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,960
is still a family of scholars.

45
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,960
How did you manage to lure

46
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:55,240
both Chen and Ye at the same time?

47
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,890
Especially Chen,

48
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,329
who even went so far as to

49
00:02:58,430 --> 00:03:00,560
reject the match proposed by Madam Fu.

50
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,630
Madam Wang,

51
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,400
are you saying Madam Fu

52
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:09,930
once arranged a match for my husband?

53
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,280
Didn't you know?

54
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,360
No, I didn't.

55
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,300
I only know that

56
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,590
my husband

57
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:18,190
invited the Senior Grand Secretary

58
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:20,360
and Madam Fu to officiate our wedding.

59
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,430
Since Madam Fu

60
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:24,000
was willing to officiate,

61
00:03:25,050 --> 00:03:27,280
it's clear that the matter of matchmaking

62
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,400
is long in the past.

63
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,660
As for you, Madam Wang,

64
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,710
my husband and I

65
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:35,840
have been married for quite some time,

66
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:37,390
but you specifically

67
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,800
bring this up today.

68
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,520
Those who know you

69
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,870
might think you're just making small talk.

70
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:43,930
But those who don't

71
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:45,079
might think you are

72
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:46,960
deliberately disrespecting Madam Fu,

73
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,470
trying to sow discord

74
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,800
between Madam Fu and me.

75
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:51,680
Don't slander me.

76
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:52,710
Enough.

77
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,590
That's not what I meant.

78
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:57,079
Madam Chen is right.

79
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,280
It's just a trivial matter.

80
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,610
I've long forgotten it.

81
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,450
We are here today

82
00:04:01,450 --> 00:04:03,230
to taste tea and relax.

83
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:06,060
There's no need
to mention the trivial details.

84
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:07,030
Indeed.

85
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,430
The pastries today

86
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:12,840
are truly excellent.

87
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:16,870
Yes,

88
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:19,870
especially this blood bird's nest.

89
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,459
It's smooth and delicate,

90
00:04:21,829 --> 00:04:22,920
very delicious.

91
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:25,560
But its appearance

92
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,520
looks somewhat like the tribute

93
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:29,630
sent from Nanyang some time ago.

94
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:32,159
What...

95
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,090
How could this be a tribute?

96
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,560
You must be mistaken.

97
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:40,510
I picked up some random pieces

98
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,970
of bird's nest from a shop.

99
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:43,760
That's impossible.

100
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,430
Earlier, someone

101
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:47,490
brought top-grade blood bird's nest

102
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,360
to my shop for consignment,

103
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,190
claiming it was surplus tribute.

104
00:04:51,190 --> 00:04:52,190
I saw that

105
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:53,390
in person.

106
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,170
The appearance

107
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,800
is the same as

108
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,900
the blood bird's nest you served.

109
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,360
But at that time, I was worried,

110
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,400
so I didn't dare accept them.

111
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:04,830
Madam Wang,

112
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,670
you should also

113
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,040
be more careful.

114
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,950
Make absolutely sure you aren't mistaken.

115
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:12,360
If it really is a tribute,

116
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:14,040
that would be bad.

117
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,630
I...

118
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,060
This...

119
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,000
Has the Court underpaid

120
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,310
the Wang family?

121
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,060
To think you would embezzle such things!

122
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:23,870
No...

123
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:24,480
Enough.

124
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:26,750
Let's treat this as an accident.

125
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:28,040
After everyone goes back,

126
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,300
please do not cause any further trouble.

127
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:31,600
Madam,

128
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:33,420
Lord Chen has arrived.

129
00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:35,880
He says he is here to pick up Madam Chen.

130
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,770
Then I shall take my leave.

131
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,430
Tribute?

132
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:07,040
I didn't want to expose her at first,

133
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,190
but this Madam Wang

134
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,190
has repeatedly

135
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,830
made things difficult for me.

136
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,830
Naturally, I won't indulge her anymore.

137
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:14,240
I absolutely did not see it wrong.

138
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,440
That was the tribute sent from Nanyang.

139
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,000
You've been wronged.

140
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:19,870
So wronged.

141
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,530
You shouldn't indulge her.

142
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,720
What's wrong?

143
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,860
I was thinking,

144
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,270
with so many state affairs,

145
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:30,200
from land reform down to tributes,

146
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:32,040
they are riddled with holes

147
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:33,690
and flaws everywhere.

148
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:37,130
Wang Xuanfan made one careless mistake,

149
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:39,450
and you actually caught his weakness.

150
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,510
Just watch.

151
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,010
This time,

152
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:44,560
he has crossed my mentor's bottom line.

153
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,820
He will fly into a rage.

154
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:51,710
[Wang Residence]

155
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,720
Idiot!

156
00:06:51,990 --> 00:06:53,650
What an absolute idiot!

157
00:06:52,670 --> 00:06:58,920
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

158
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:55,310
You...

159
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,510
What were you thinking?

160
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,120
What were you thinking

161
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:02,310
using blood bird's nest to entertain them?

162
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:02,950
Are you

163
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:03,870
tired of being a Grand Secretary's wife?

164
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:05,730
You're pushing me into a fire pit!

165
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,700
How was I supposed to know?

166
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:09,850
It's boiled and put in a bowl,

167
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:10,980
yet she could still

168
00:07:10,980 --> 00:07:12,860
know that it's a tribute.

169
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,630
That Gu Jinzhao,

170
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:16,160
what is her tongue made of?

171
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:18,030
How could she taste that?

172
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,870
She comes from a wealthy family.

173
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:22,360
What hasn't she eaten?

174
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,240
All you do

175
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,510
is look down on merchants.

176
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:26,240
She's eaten more salt

177
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,570
than you've eaten rice!

178
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,600
I look down on merchants?

179
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,830
Do you respect them?

180
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,040
I respect no one,

181
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,510
but I respect wealth.

182
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:38,630
You...

183
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:40,920
You must

184
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,600
retrieve the consigned tributes

185
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,680
immediately.

186
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,820
Is it really that serious?

187
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,720
Madam Fu already said

188
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,970
this was just an accident,

189
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,240
and told everyone

190
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:53,159
not to cause further trouble.

191
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:54,360
She was just paying lip service,

192
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,090
and you actually believed her?

193
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,510
Over the years, she and
the Senior Grand Secretary

194
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:58,600
have played good cop, bad cop.

195
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,600
Have you still not figured that out?

196
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,680
I was just recently involved

197
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,630
in the scholars' riot,

198
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:04,720
which offended the Senior Grand Secretary.

199
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,160
I was counting on you

200
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,330
to coax his wife,

201
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,680
so Madam Fu could use some pillow talk.

202
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,510
But instead,

203
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,310
you drop this disaster on me.

204
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:14,040
Are you God's punishment

205
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,390
for me?

206
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,070
I'm your punishment?

207
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,270
Wang Xuanfan,

208
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:20,930
you better explain yourself.

209
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:22,800
Even the money for you
to travel to the capital for the exams

210
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,700
was provided by my family.

211
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,240
Without me,

212
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:28,160
would you be where you are today?

213
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,510
How dare you!

214
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,190
When you needed me,

215
00:08:31,210 --> 00:08:32,700
I was your darling.

216
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,960
Now that you don't,

217
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,850
I'm your punishment!

218
00:08:35,909 --> 00:08:37,750
And you call yourself a Grand Secretary?

219
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:39,470
How can you be so shameless?

220
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:41,559
You are nothing but a village boor!

221
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,840
Alright, alright.

222
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,630
Calm down. Don't be angry.

223
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,600
I'm sorry.

224
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,480
Look, here's the plan.

225
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:49,700
Right now,

226
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,080
go immediately and

227
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:53,360
clean up all the loose ends
regarding the tributes.

228
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,360
I'll make another trip

229
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,750
to the Senior Grand Secretary's residence.

230
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:57,600
What for?

231
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,840
What else?

232
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,730
To admit my mistake.

233
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:05,960
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

234
00:09:07,740 --> 00:09:09,580
Chen and his wife

235
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,980
are really so annoying.

236
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:19,120
Does Lord Wang

237
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,630
admire an official

238
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:22,000
named Zeng Ruoyu?

239
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:24,870
Lord Zeng is the Chancellor
of the National Academy.

240
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:26,530
He is Wang's fellow townsman.

241
00:09:26,950 --> 00:09:28,210
Why do you bring him up?

242
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:30,240
I know

243
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,910
Wang wants to recommend Lord Zeng

244
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:33,390
to become the Vice Minister of Rites.

245
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:34,360
And Lord Yao

246
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:36,170
even promised to vote for him.

247
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:37,920
How do you know this?

248
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:39,790
I also know

249
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,200
Grand Secretary Shen

250
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,860
was reprimanded
by the Senior Grand Secretary.

251
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,510
That was last month.

252
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:48,910
Where did you hear all this from?

253
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:49,710
The tea party?

254
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:53,550
I thought these madams

255
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:55,030
would chat about things like

256
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:55,870
the Classic for Girls or whatever

257
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:57,000
at tea parties.

258
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:58,360
I never expected

259
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,200
that what they discussed

260
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,860
were entirely court affairs.

261
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:03,080
And I even saw

262
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,320
Madam Fu comforting Madam Shen, saying

263
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:06,960
that the Senior Grand Secretary

264
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,510
still trusts Grand Secretary Shen,

265
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:09,910
telling her not to worry.

266
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:12,510
So it turns out the tea party

267
00:10:12,510 --> 00:10:13,970
has this kind of function.

268
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,000
Interesting.

269
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:17,000
Yes.

270
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,360
I think it's even more interesting

271
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,560
than doing business.

272
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,000
Each madam sitting there

273
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,400
is practically a Grand Secretary herself.

274
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:25,590
A Madam Secretariat.

275
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,000
How can you say that?

276
00:10:28,670 --> 00:10:30,400
That's treasonous, Lord Chen.

277
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:38,150
I know you like the tea party,

278
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,720
but do you know

279
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,510
if the term Madam Secretariat

280
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:44,390
reaches the ears of the imperial censors,

281
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:45,450
what would happen?

282
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:47,920
You don't want me to go again?

283
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,270
Of course not.

284
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,860
I'm just reminding you

285
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,520
to be careful.

286
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:54,630
I know.

287
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:57,350
Besides, I've already asked around.

288
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:59,240
The tea parties started several years ago

289
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:01,100
and have been going on ever since.

290
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,360
Moreover, these Grand Secretaries

291
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,510
use their wives

292
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,840
to exchange information with each other.

293
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,960
You've been following
Senior Grand Secretary

294
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:08,960
for so many years,

295
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:11,450
yet you didn't know about the tea parties.

296
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:13,210
Exactly.

297
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:14,810
It's a huge loss for me.

298
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,370
Luckily, I found out today.

299
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,150
That's why

300
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,780
I was so eager to marry you.

301
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,590
Gu Jinzhao.

302
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:35,950
Look at my lips.

303
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:38,430
I need to go
to Linxia Restaurant tomorrow.

304
00:12:54,790 --> 00:12:55,520
Third Uncle.

305
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,480
Why are you here?

306
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,140
What's the matter?

307
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,010
It's about those scholars.

308
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,670
I heard some rumors

309
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:06,090
that might be disadvantageous to you.

310
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,060
I'll be right back.

311
00:13:13,510 --> 00:13:14,640
You go inside first.

312
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:18,110
Follow me.

313
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:36,840
My Lady.

314
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,320
This...

315
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:45,480
Throw this away,

316
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:46,950
far away.

317
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,120
The farther, the better.

318
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:48,600
Yes.

319
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,800
What's wrong?

320
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:55,070
Did someone plead for leniency?

321
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,390
Yes.

322
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,200
I dare not hide it from you, Third Uncle.

323
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,870
Indeed, the families

324
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:04,600
and teachers of some scholars came to me,

325
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:06,060
but I turned them all away.

326
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:07,360
However,

327
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,660
I've also heard some rumors outside.

328
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:11,960
They say you disregard the Court's laws

329
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,240
and detain those scholars

330
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,770
in the Shuntian Prefecture

331
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,060
just to vent your personal anger.

332
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:19,930
Personal anger?

333
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:22,870
Even if it is,

334
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:24,670
it's not entirely wrong.

335
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:28,440
I'm afraid imperial censors
might impeach you.

336
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,600
So you came to me

337
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,030
to ask me

338
00:14:31,030 --> 00:14:32,560
to release those scholars?

339
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:36,120
You are perceptive, Third Uncle.

340
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,270
The reason those scholars

341
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:38,750
did such a thing was entirely

342
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:40,240
out of a moment of righteous indignation.

343
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,570
What do you mean by that?

344
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,510
Just the fact that they could precisely

345
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:45,110
block my carriage on the road

346
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:47,670
shows it wasn't just pure impulse,

347
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:48,240
not to mention

348
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,810
those flags and banners.

349
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:50,670
If they hadn't prepared

350
00:14:50,670 --> 00:14:51,390
a day or two in advance,

351
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:52,840
it would have been impossible.

352
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,600
You jump to conclusions

353
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:55,270
about things you haven't seen

354
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,500
with your own eyes.

355
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:58,010
Are you being foolish,

356
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,920
or do you have ulterior motives?

357
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:03,750
I was wrong.

358
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,240
I shouldn't have easily believed

359
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,170
their nonsense.

360
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,120
Please forgive me, Third Uncle.

361
00:15:14,390 --> 00:15:15,990
You are an ambitious person.

362
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,670
But the greatest weakness
for ambitious people

363
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:19,270
is having high aims
but lacking the talent.

364
00:15:19,270 --> 00:15:21,670
If you pick up the habit
of being self-righteous

365
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,510
and believing every rumor you hear,

366
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:25,440
how can you enter the Cabinet
in the future?

367
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:27,550
You won't even get your foot in the door.

368
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:28,120
Get up.

369
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:35,390
You don't need to
worry about this anymore.

370
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:36,840
If life in the Hanlin Academy

371
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,100
is far too idle for you,

372
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,810
you can think about your marriage.

373
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,960
The Yu family has urged us many times.

374
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,720
Within this year,

375
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:47,250
we'll arrange the wedding
for you and Wanxue.

376
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:48,510
Yes.

377
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,510
Then I shall

378
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:55,280
take my leave first.

379
00:15:55,550 --> 00:15:56,150
You may go.

380
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:09,840
Xuanqing?

381
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,160
Third Master,

382
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,080
what happened?

383
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:24,240
Xuanqing came to me just now.

384
00:16:24,510 --> 00:16:26,120
He clearly wanted to plead

385
00:16:26,270 --> 00:16:28,150
for the scholars
who blocked my sedan chair.

386
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:29,200
But he seemed to have no idea

387
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,510
how to speak for them.

388
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,670
It felt more like
a spur-of-the-moment decision.

389
00:16:33,670 --> 00:16:34,670
Enough about him.

390
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:36,480
How is it?

391
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,910
Wang Xuanfan's embezzlement
of the tributes

392
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,570
has been fully investigated.

393
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:44,440
Here.

394
00:16:45,290 --> 00:16:48,080
[To the Honorable Master]

395
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:49,000
Every year, the tributes from all regions

396
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,060
are first sent to the Wang residence.

397
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,340
The Wang family opened a store
in the capital

398
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:54,080
to sell specialties from the south,

399
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,320
claiming to exclusively
sell surplus tributes,

400
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,180
but they are the actual tributes.

401
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,710
This man is incredibly audacious.

402
00:16:58,710 --> 00:16:59,050
[My investigation of the tribute officials and escorts]

403
00:16:59,080 --> 00:16:59,500
[confirms that upon the annual tributes' arrival in the capital,]

404
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,750
Should we arrange for someone

405
00:16:59,520 --> 00:16:59,890
[a portion must first be diverted to the Wang residence.]

406
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:00,350
[The ledger records tributes like
Nanyang blood bird's nest and Fujian rock tea;]

407
00:17:00,370 --> 00:17:00,840
[these transactions, when cross-checked with the imperial registry,]

408
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:01,360
[show exact matches in patterns and styles across many items.]

409
00:17:00,900 --> 00:17:01,760
to impeach him?

410
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:06,960
Same as last time.

411
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,680
Just impeach him.

412
00:17:08,829 --> 00:17:10,230
Don't be too aggressive,

413
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:12,069
and don't pursue it relentlessly.

414
00:17:12,069 --> 00:17:12,800
Understood.

415
00:17:13,790 --> 00:17:15,010
Just a light tap.

416
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:15,720
Exactly.

417
00:17:21,349 --> 00:17:22,400
My mentor regards Wang Xuanfan

418
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,680
as his right-hand man.

419
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,619
To get rid of him,

420
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:28,550
we need to take slow, steady steps,

421
00:17:28,550 --> 00:17:30,510
wearing him down bit by bit.

422
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:35,720
In the disaster relief grain case,

423
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:36,750
Madam Wang

424
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:39,510
took dividends from the grain merchants.

425
00:17:39,510 --> 00:17:40,720
That's one piece lost.

426
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:43,400
Wang Xuanfan incited the scholars
to block my sedan chair,

427
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,600
angering His Majesty

428
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:47,330
and disrupting the land reform.

429
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,140
That's three pieces lost.

430
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:57,640
Wang Xuanfan

431
00:17:57,850 --> 00:17:59,140
embezzled tributes.

432
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:01,800
That's another piece lost.

433
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:13,680
It seems

434
00:18:14,590 --> 00:18:16,450
a couple more strikes are needed.

435
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:17,960
Soon.

436
00:18:25,730 --> 00:18:28,870
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

437
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:29,830
Get out!

438
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:32,090
Did I tell you to come in?

439
00:18:32,090 --> 00:18:33,550
You have no manners at all!

440
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:38,960
Please calm your anger, Yuanweng.

441
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:41,000
Actually, the Senior Grand Secretary

442
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,000
treats you as one of his own,

443
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:45,270
which is why he was so blunt.

444
00:18:45,390 --> 00:18:48,650
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

445
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:46,850
You call that blunt?

446
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,830
That was a slap in the face!

447
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,630
Slapping me time and time again!

448
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:55,550
Last time it was
in front of Third Mr. Chen,

449
00:18:55,550 --> 00:18:57,310
this time it was in front of His Majesty.

450
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:58,070
Just because a few

451
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:59,160
ignorant scholars shouted a few words

452
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,680
about liquidating the imperial estates,

453
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,030
he... he reprimanded me,

454
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:04,400
saying I was acting out
and told me to step down!

455
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,240
Haven't I done enough

456
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,830
for land reform?

457
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:08,480
I gave so much money

458
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:09,880
to make up for it the moment he asked.

459
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:11,260
Wasn't it all for him?

460
00:19:24,670 --> 00:19:25,930
Actually I don't blame

461
00:19:27,790 --> 00:19:29,400
the Senior Grand Secretary.

462
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:30,910
He had no choice.

463
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:32,670
He was put on the spot by Chen.

464
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:33,790
Exactly.

465
00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:36,060
In this scholar riot,

466
00:19:36,310 --> 00:19:37,350
if Chen Yanyun truly

467
00:19:37,350 --> 00:19:39,030
considered the bigger picture,

468
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:40,000
he could have easily

469
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,440
covered the matter up right there.

470
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,550
But instead,

471
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:45,270
he sent the scholars and their banners

472
00:19:45,270 --> 00:19:47,490
straight to the Shuntian Prefecture.

473
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:48,550
It's such a huge incident.

474
00:19:48,550 --> 00:19:49,960
I couldn't keep it hidden either,

475
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,270
so I had to report it upwards.

476
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,420
Alright, alright.

477
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:55,210
I'm not blaming you either.

478
00:19:58,320 --> 00:20:01,410
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

479
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:08,340
I reflected carefully.

480
00:20:09,130 --> 00:20:10,310
If I'm not mistaken,

481
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:14,400
ever since he took down Fan Chuan
in the disaster relief grain case,

482
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,200
Chen had already

483
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,460
started targeting me.

484
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:17,960
He resented me for making him

485
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:20,000
take the blame for the grain swap.

486
00:20:22,030 --> 00:20:23,740
So narrow-minded.

487
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:35,970
We've been talking for so long.

488
00:20:36,270 --> 00:20:37,510
I'm getting tired.

489
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:44,120
Then we shall take our leave.

490
00:20:47,270 --> 00:20:48,460
Hold on, Ziliang.

491
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,930
I have something to ask you.

492
00:21:11,030 --> 00:21:12,030
I remember Gu Deyuan, the Censorate's

493
00:21:12,030 --> 00:21:13,690
Assistant Censor-in-Chief,

494
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,000
was previously involved in

495
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:17,550
the embezzlement case of Zeng Yanqiu,
the Vice Minister of Works.

496
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:19,280
Later, it was left unresolved.

497
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,680
A person used to taking bribes

498
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:25,450
can never restrain themselves.

499
00:21:25,450 --> 00:21:27,400
Now that he has become in-laws with Chen,

500
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,680
with such a big backer,

501
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:32,200
I think he's going to make a move again.

502
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,270
Yes.

503
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:36,200
However,

504
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:38,880
why didn't you hand this over to Lord Yao?

505
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:40,000
Wouldn't it be more convenient

506
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,550
for the Ministry of Justice
to investigate this?

507
00:21:41,550 --> 00:21:43,160
Gu Deyuan's daughter

508
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:46,480
is married to Yao Ping's youngest son.

509
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,030
Zhao,

510
00:22:08,310 --> 00:22:09,400
we've selected a few varieties

511
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,550
of newly released tea.

512
00:22:10,550 --> 00:22:11,830
We can't quite make up our minds,

513
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:13,490
so we'd like you to take a look.

514
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:15,950
Lan,

515
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:17,920
preparing for the Linxia Restaurant

516
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,720
involves a lot of trivial matters.

517
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:21,180
Thanks for your hard work.

518
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:25,800
[Snow Orchid Breaths on Jade] [Twilight Lotus Diffuses Scent]

519
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:25,060
During my home visit this time,

520
00:22:25,060 --> 00:22:26,440
I didn't go back to Daxin.

521
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,510
Did they make things difficult for you?

522
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:29,790
It was alright, actually.

523
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:31,850
Grandmother didn't even bring it up.

524
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:33,240
Second Aunt and Lian

525
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,300
made a few remarks.

526
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:36,730
I didn't care about them at all.

527
00:22:37,270 --> 00:22:38,030
However,

528
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:40,400
I do have a favor

529
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,550
to ask of you.

530
00:22:42,790 --> 00:22:43,560
Go ahead.

531
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,820
I want to move back to Sili Hutong.

532
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:48,070
Now that you've married
into the Chen Mansion,

533
00:22:48,070 --> 00:22:49,200
Father has been assigned
outside the capital,

534
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:50,030
and Rong is always

535
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:51,380
at the Qifang Hutong Academy.

536
00:22:51,380 --> 00:22:53,270
It's just me alone in the ancestral home,

537
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:54,530
which is quite boring.

538
00:22:58,070 --> 00:22:59,470
That is indeed an option.

539
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:02,290
However, you need to think it through.

540
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,070
After all, you are an

541
00:23:04,070 --> 00:23:05,240
unmarried lady.

542
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,860
Setting up a household on your own

543
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:10,270
will inevitably invite gossip.

544
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:11,370
I'm not afraid.

545
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:14,080
I just want to live more freely,

546
00:23:14,270 --> 00:23:16,270
which is better than anything else.

547
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:18,110
Since you've thought it through,

548
00:23:18,110 --> 00:23:19,270
then go ahead and move.

549
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,830
The property deed for Sili Hutong

550
00:23:20,830 --> 00:23:21,590
is with me.

551
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:23,720
You have a share.

552
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,150
If you have spare money,

553
00:23:26,350 --> 00:23:28,000
I can sell my share to you too.

554
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:30,750
Consider it as acquiring an estate.

555
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,500
That's wonderful!

556
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:35,600
Thank you.

557
00:23:35,750 --> 00:23:36,430
Sit down.

558
00:23:39,550 --> 00:23:40,720
[Twilight Lotus Diffuses Scent
]

559
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,280
By the way,

560
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:44,840
do you still remember

561
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,620
Mu Zhidi?

562
00:23:47,830 --> 00:23:48,790
The one who

563
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,160
looks a bit silly?

564
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,240
His father,

565
00:23:51,350 --> 00:23:52,440
Lord Mu Shi'an,

566
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:55,280
is a longtime friend
of your brother-in-law.

567
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:56,310
This time,

568
00:23:56,510 --> 00:23:57,770
he brought it up again.

569
00:23:58,030 --> 00:23:59,560
I told your brother-in-law

570
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:01,880
that when they brought it up
the year before last,

571
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:03,280
you had already refused.

572
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:04,510
Your brother-in-law

573
00:24:04,510 --> 00:24:05,890
knows all of this.

574
00:24:06,350 --> 00:24:07,000
Then,

575
00:24:07,550 --> 00:24:08,640
what does he think?

576
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:10,590
Your brother-in-law says

577
00:24:10,590 --> 00:24:11,590
Mr. Mu

578
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,850
is a decent person,

579
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:15,590
and Mu family has a good reputation.

580
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:16,880
However,

581
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,610
marriage is a lifelong matter.

582
00:24:19,270 --> 00:24:21,060
You must think it through

583
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,220
and don't force it.

584
00:24:23,440 --> 00:24:25,300
Since my brother-in-law says so,

585
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:26,310
then,

586
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:27,240
could you

587
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:28,700
arrange for Mu Zhidi and me

588
00:24:28,790 --> 00:24:29,510
to meet?

589
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:30,310
Sure.

590
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:32,690
Then I'll pick a suitable time

591
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,160
for you two to meet.

592
00:24:34,510 --> 00:24:36,170
We'll talk more about it then.

593
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:40,520
By the way,

594
00:24:42,070 --> 00:24:43,160
I heard

595
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:46,270
Ye Xian has been acting like a madman,

596
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:49,130
angering quite a few court officials.

597
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:50,350
It's true?

598
00:24:56,870 --> 00:25:01,710
[Ye Residence]

599
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,270
Pass it down to him?

600
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:23,450
Can he even swing it?

601
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:25,530
Look at his frail physique,

602
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:28,680
he can forget about
wielding a sword in this lifetime!

603
00:25:33,790 --> 00:25:35,890
Fu Hailian is absolutely determined

604
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,270
to see me dead.

605
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:39,400
And you came in to accompany me?

606
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,830
Do you think you're being a filial son?

607
00:25:40,830 --> 00:25:41,790
Foolish!

608
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,960
Figure out a way to get out of here.

609
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:46,020
Protect your mother and your sister.

610
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:48,820
If the Marquis's mansion is gone,
so be it.

611
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,130
You never wanted

612
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:53,000
to inherit the title anyway.

613
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:35,190
It's very kind of you to think of my lord,

614
00:26:35,190 --> 00:26:36,880
and even invite a renowned doctor.

615
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:38,160
It's just that lately,

616
00:26:38,830 --> 00:26:40,830
his temper has become more eccentric.

617
00:26:40,830 --> 00:26:42,510
If he speaks harshly,

618
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:44,510
please bear with him.

619
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:49,350
Don't I know his temper well enough?

620
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:50,680
Don't worry about that.

621
00:26:53,350 --> 00:26:55,000
My Lord, Miss Xue is here.

622
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:56,440
She specially brought a renowned doctor.

623
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:57,160
Ye Xian!

624
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:58,270
My Lord!

625
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,110
Doctor,

626
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,960
My lord has already finished his medicine.

627
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:33,560
Why isn't he getting better?

628
00:27:36,690 --> 00:27:38,090
What exactly is going on?

629
00:27:38,510 --> 00:27:39,770
Please speak frankly.

630
00:27:40,550 --> 00:27:42,640
His chronic illness is hard to cure.

631
00:27:43,510 --> 00:27:45,200
I'm afraid his life

632
00:27:46,350 --> 00:27:47,880
won't last much longer.

633
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:48,550
What?

634
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,070
Doctor,

635
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,760
I beg you, please save him!

636
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:53,540
I'll kowtow to you, Doctor!

637
00:27:53,570 --> 00:27:54,240
Please get up quickly.

638
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,640
-I beg you!
-Doctor Zhou,

639
00:27:56,870 --> 00:27:59,000
if I ask you to treat him
with all your might,

640
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,130
how long can he live?

641
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,270
At most,

642
00:28:05,310 --> 00:28:06,680
three years.

643
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:12,590
Three years?

644
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:15,660
Don't cry here.

645
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:19,440
Ruixiang,

646
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:21,310
take Doctor Zhou
to write the prescription.

647
00:28:21,310 --> 00:28:21,920
Yes.

648
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:34,440
You're awake?

649
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:52,510
Actually...

650
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:54,510
actually, Doctor Zhou's

651
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,960
prognosis might not be accurate.

652
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:57,000
We need to consult a few more doctors

653
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:57,900
to be certain.

654
00:28:58,440 --> 00:29:00,680
I heard there's an imperial physician
in Songjiang Prefecture...

655
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:01,740
Don't tell anyone.

656
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:09,530
The fact that I only have
three years to live.

657
00:29:12,070 --> 00:29:14,070
I hope you can keep it a secret for me.

658
00:29:14,750 --> 00:29:15,980
Didn't I just say?

659
00:29:16,010 --> 00:29:17,000
What Doctor Zhou said

660
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:17,550
might not be accurate.

661
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,680
-He is right.
-He...

662
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,030
Three years

663
00:29:24,060 --> 00:29:24,740
is enough.

664
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:39,770
Where are you going?

665
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,070
Shut up.

666
00:29:44,510 --> 00:29:47,040
Were you going to say
it's none of my business?

667
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:49,510
I just saved your life,

668
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:51,510
and you'd better have a conscience.

669
00:29:55,510 --> 00:29:57,440
I'm going to Zhending Prefecture.

670
00:29:59,510 --> 00:30:00,240
For work?

671
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:03,400
In your condition,

672
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:04,720
how can you work?

673
00:30:06,270 --> 00:30:07,270
Let me go with you.

674
00:30:09,160 --> 00:30:09,720
Didn't you say

675
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:11,180
I should keep your secret?

676
00:30:11,510 --> 00:30:12,710
Then take me with you.

677
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,550
Otherwise,

678
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:17,290
if I get drunk one day,

679
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:18,030
and accidentally slip up,

680
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:19,560
I might just tell everyone.

681
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,310
You're back?

682
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,540
You're late today.

683
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,200
I had already finished my shift,

684
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:05,270
but my mentor suddenly remembered
the river project,

685
00:31:05,270 --> 00:31:07,000
and insisted on discussing it.

686
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,370
This discussion

687
00:31:08,750 --> 00:31:10,010
took four whole hours.

688
00:31:29,990 --> 00:31:31,390
Seeing you look like this

689
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:33,000
reminds me

690
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:34,160
of an idiom.

691
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:35,560
What is it?

692
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:41,930
Standing by with folded arms.

693
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,070
Listen to that,

694
00:31:45,750 --> 00:31:46,510
someone is

695
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:48,840
complaining that I'm not a virtuous wife.

696
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:53,350
Let me attend to Lord Chen right now.

697
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:56,750
Let me serve you well.

698
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,350
-Lord Chen,
-That's more like it.

699
00:32:03,350 --> 00:32:04,410
please have a seat.

700
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,530
Let's see where you can run.

701
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:28,070
What should we do?

702
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,410
Yanyun didn't marry

703
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:30,920
a virtuous wife.

704
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:33,210
You don't need to be virtuous.

705
00:32:33,310 --> 00:32:34,640
This is perfectly fine.

706
00:32:35,270 --> 00:32:36,120
I like it.

707
00:32:39,990 --> 00:32:40,910
Besides,

708
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,660
you have other strengths.

709
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:44,960
What?

710
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,200
Guess.

711
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:49,920
You're rich.

712
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:51,200
Hey.

713
00:32:57,590 --> 00:32:58,350
Don't move.

714
00:32:58,790 --> 00:33:00,320
Let me hold you a bit longer.

715
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:06,590
What's wrong?

716
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:07,770
Tired today?

717
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:08,890
I'm alright,

718
00:33:10,550 --> 00:33:12,010
just need to hold you more.

719
00:33:20,230 --> 00:33:20,830
By the way,

720
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,420
Mother fell ill today,

721
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:25,720
but she didn't call for a physician.

722
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:27,880
Do you want to go take a look?

723
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:34,310
No need.

724
00:33:35,270 --> 00:33:36,060
Last night,

725
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:38,040
I already told her the truth.

726
00:33:39,550 --> 00:33:40,310
No wonder.

727
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:48,640
Tell me,

728
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,640
how could Yanwen

729
00:33:52,790 --> 00:33:53,830
do...

730
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,590
do

731
00:33:56,590 --> 00:33:58,790
such things?

732
00:34:01,580 --> 00:34:02,940
Since he was little,

733
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:07,780
I hired renowned teachers for him,

734
00:34:09,150 --> 00:34:10,510
and gave him

735
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:13,030
the exact same education

736
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:15,429
like his brothers.

737
00:34:15,550 --> 00:34:17,760
You must not blame yourself.

738
00:34:18,510 --> 00:34:19,590
They say a dragon has nine sons,

739
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:21,190
and each one is uniquely different.

740
00:34:21,190 --> 00:34:22,920
If Fourth Master grew up astray,

741
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:24,449
how could anyone blame you?

742
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:25,760
Besides,

743
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:27,980
if you ask around the entire capital,

744
00:34:28,070 --> 00:34:31,270
no one raises the younger generations
better than you do.

745
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:32,880
Not to mention Third Master,

746
00:34:33,150 --> 00:34:34,510
who is highly respected
as a Grand Secretary.

747
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:35,190
Second Master,

748
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:36,960
is also a high-ranking
provincial official.

749
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,920
And in the next generation,

750
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:38,949
Xuanqing,

751
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:40,920
is a dignified Tanhua scholar.

752
00:34:41,110 --> 00:34:41,909
In the future,

753
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:44,330
he might also become
a Cabinet Minister.

754
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:49,860
As long as you keep an open mind,

755
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,440
and don't dwell on a dead end,

756
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,659
your days

757
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:55,130
will surely be harmonious and beautiful.

758
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:57,280
I know.

759
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,800
Actually,

760
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,820
Mother had long suspected

761
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,660
that he harmed Fifth Brother.

762
00:35:06,030 --> 00:35:07,960
She just didn't want to believe it.

763
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:11,280
Yesterday,

764
00:35:13,510 --> 00:35:14,680
when I told her

765
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:15,760
that he was the one who hired people

766
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:16,960
to kidnap you,

767
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:20,300
she understood everything.

768
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,320
She even asked

769
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,470
if Fourth Brother

770
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,440
will never come back again.

771
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:32,040
You don't need to worry.

772
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,800
With Mother's personality,

773
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:36,190
in a couple of days,

774
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:38,060
she'll be able to

775
00:35:38,190 --> 00:35:39,760
step out decently again

776
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:42,240
and be the respected matriarch.

777
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:49,040
Every family has its own difficulties.

778
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,920
But in our family

779
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:55,780
things are not difficult.

780
00:36:06,410 --> 00:36:08,320
[Gu Mansion]

781
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:10,570
[Moonlit Seclusion]

782
00:36:12,830 --> 00:36:15,730
[Blessings Passed Down for Generations]

783
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:17,280
Zhao!

784
00:36:19,980 --> 00:36:22,230
[Blessings Passed Down for Generations]

785
00:36:20,630 --> 00:36:21,480
Lan,

786
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,230
congratulations!

787
00:36:22,350 --> 00:36:25,850
[Snow from Yingzhong]

788
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:24,630
You move to your new home!

789
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:25,800
Thank you.

790
00:36:26,590 --> 00:36:28,350
Yanying was going to come too,

791
00:36:28,510 --> 00:36:29,720
but for no reasons,

792
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:30,670
starting from today,

793
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:32,510
she's been having an upset stomach.

794
00:36:32,510 --> 00:36:34,280
Perhaps she was greedy last night,

795
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:35,880
and had too many cold things.

796
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:36,920
So as for her gift,

797
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,780
she had to ask me to bring it to you.

798
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:40,480
There will be many
opportunities in the future.

799
00:36:40,480 --> 00:36:43,010
Next time I will send her
another invitation.

800
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:44,630
Where is Wanxue?

801
00:36:46,510 --> 00:36:47,510
She should be here soon.

802
00:36:47,490 --> 00:36:50,020
[Blessings Passed Down for Generations]

803
00:36:48,250 --> 00:36:49,390
I'm here!

804
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:55,420
Just before leaving the house,

805
00:36:55,420 --> 00:36:55,920
my stepmother

806
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,280
suddenly asked about my embroidery.

807
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,800
If I hadn't prepared in advance,

808
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:00,930
I fear I would have missed lunch today.

809
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:02,280
Dear Lan,

810
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,670
congratulations on your new home.

811
00:37:03,670 --> 00:37:04,590
Thank you.

812
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:06,840
With her here,

813
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:08,640
it's definitely going to be fun.

814
00:37:10,510 --> 00:37:11,410
Is Mr. Mu

815
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,550
also coming today?

816
00:37:17,670 --> 00:37:18,840
What are you afraid of?

817
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:20,900
You are the head of the household now.

818
00:37:20,930 --> 00:37:21,810
He's coming over

819
00:37:21,810 --> 00:37:23,630
to congratulate you on your new home too.

820
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:24,400
You should

821
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:26,280
greet him naturally.

822
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:29,450
Zhao, please come with me.

823
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:30,480
Alright.

824
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:35,110
My Lady, Mr. Mu has arrived.

825
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:00,280
Xuanqing!

826
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:20,150
[Harmony Brings Blessings]

827
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:36,950
Mu Zhidi

828
00:38:37,270 --> 00:38:39,330
bowed about eighteen times already.

829
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,480
Poor thing.

830
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:42,510
Since you invited him over,

831
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:44,070
you can't just not say a single word,

832
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:45,930
and ignore him like this, can you?

833
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:46,960
I...

834
00:38:47,230 --> 00:38:48,630
I don't know what to say.

835
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:01,760
Wanxue,

836
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:05,510
this is your first time in this residence?

837
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,710
I'll show you around.

838
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:07,710
Okay!

839
00:39:21,760 --> 00:39:22,590
In that case,

840
00:39:25,030 --> 00:39:26,230
I'll go for a walk too.

841
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:41,190
Mr. Mu,

842
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:42,560
how about

843
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:44,070
we go for a walk too?

844
00:39:44,230 --> 00:39:45,230
Sure, sure.

845
00:40:05,110 --> 00:40:06,070
Mr. Mu,

846
00:40:06,610 --> 00:40:08,380
my inviting you here this time

847
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:11,360
is actually not a genuine attempt
at matchmaking.

848
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,280
Rather,

849
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:13,960
I didn't want to brush off my sister

850
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:16,220
and brother-in-law's good intentions.

851
00:40:19,670 --> 00:40:20,590
I have actually

852
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:21,960
made up my mind

853
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:23,400
to never marry.

854
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:24,510
Why?

855
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,660
You should know my situation.

856
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:30,400
My father was demoted
to Pingyang Prefecture,

857
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:31,730
and my mom made a mistake

858
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:34,010
and is still locked up to this day.

859
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:36,580
I also made many mistakes in the past.

860
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:39,550
Thanks to my sister
for forgiving my past misdeeds.

861
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:40,510
In short,

862
00:40:40,670 --> 00:40:41,550
if I wanted to marry

863
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:42,760
someone of a higher status,

864
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:44,220
they wouldn't care for me,

865
00:40:44,510 --> 00:40:46,670
and I wouldn't
force myself on them either.

866
00:40:46,670 --> 00:40:47,870
If I settled for less,

867
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:49,090
I wouldn't be happy.

868
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,190
It's better to be alone

869
00:40:50,190 --> 00:40:51,590
and live a peaceful life.

870
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:52,840
Now,

871
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:53,840
I just want to learn from my sister

872
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,440
how to do business properly,

873
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:56,850
and save up more money.

874
00:40:57,190 --> 00:40:57,990
In the future,

875
00:40:58,510 --> 00:40:59,710
when my mom grows old,

876
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:01,510
I will beg Old Madam Ji

877
00:41:01,670 --> 00:41:03,870
and bring her out so I can serve her well.

878
00:41:04,030 --> 00:41:06,230
I would be content with that for my life.

879
00:41:12,510 --> 00:41:12,960
You...

880
00:41:13,590 --> 00:41:15,390
why aren't you saying anything?

881
00:41:16,110 --> 00:41:16,590
I...

882
00:41:18,030 --> 00:41:19,670
I am a clumsy speaker.

883
00:41:20,510 --> 00:41:22,070
You have been through so much.

884
00:41:22,070 --> 00:41:23,330
If I were in your shoes,

885
00:41:23,590 --> 00:41:24,110
I would be exactly the same,

886
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:25,770
only wanting to live on my own.

887
00:41:27,550 --> 00:41:28,360
But I truly

888
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,060
feel sorry for you.

889
00:41:39,070 --> 00:41:39,840
So...

890
00:41:40,510 --> 00:41:42,000
so... so I really don't know

891
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:42,930
what else to say.

892
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:53,050
I... I brought some people with me.

893
00:41:53,230 --> 00:41:54,840
They are waiting outside.

894
00:41:56,880 --> 00:41:58,540
Why did you bring people over?

895
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:00,760
I wanted...

896
00:42:04,030 --> 00:42:05,760
to give you a pond of lucky fish.

897
00:42:06,230 --> 00:42:07,880
Give me a pond of lucky fish?

898
00:42:08,550 --> 00:42:09,280
A few days ago,

899
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:10,760
when I received your invitation,

900
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:11,940
I went to find Rong.

901
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:12,800
I asked him

902
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:14,060
what exactly you like.

903
00:42:14,590 --> 00:42:15,630
Rong said,

904
00:42:15,630 --> 00:42:16,920
since you were pampered from a young age,

905
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:17,950
you lack nothing.

906
00:42:18,150 --> 00:42:19,920
But after Madam Chen
arrived in the capital,

907
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:21,280
your mother kept a pond of lucky fish

908
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:22,400
in her courtyard,

909
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:25,030
which you admired for a long time.

910
00:42:25,030 --> 00:42:25,960
So,

911
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:27,440
I thought

912
00:42:28,110 --> 00:42:29,700
I would also build a pond

913
00:42:30,190 --> 00:42:31,250
in your courtyard,

914
00:42:31,440 --> 00:42:33,290
and keep some lucky fish in it.

915
00:42:33,440 --> 00:42:34,760
This way, when you have free time,

916
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:36,030
you can watch the fish,

917
00:42:36,710 --> 00:42:38,910
and your heart might feel a bit lighter.

918
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:40,030
I...

919
00:42:41,190 --> 00:42:43,050
also called some craftsmen over.

920
00:42:43,190 --> 00:42:44,110
Earlier, I was

921
00:42:44,710 --> 00:42:46,030
afraid it would be too presumptuous

922
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:47,030
and scare you,

923
00:42:47,230 --> 00:42:47,920
so I...

924
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:50,210
didn't let them in.

925
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,860
You went through a lot of trouble.

926
00:42:55,670 --> 00:42:56,220
Then...

927
00:42:56,920 --> 00:42:58,260
let them come in.

928
00:42:58,320 --> 00:42:59,070
Sure!

929
00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:01,320
But...

930
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:07,060
Let me lead the way.

931
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:08,150
Okay.

932
00:43:11,630 --> 00:43:13,360
Is Lord Chen treating you well?

933
00:43:14,030 --> 00:43:14,670
Yes.

934
00:43:15,400 --> 00:43:16,430
That's good.

935
00:43:16,550 --> 00:43:17,880
I am truly happy for you.

936
00:43:18,760 --> 00:43:19,760
I was quite nervous

937
00:43:19,760 --> 00:43:21,650
about getting married.

938
00:43:22,030 --> 00:43:23,190
But the moment I think about

939
00:43:23,190 --> 00:43:24,510
you being in the Chen family,

940
00:43:24,510 --> 00:43:25,710
I don't worry as much.

941
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:27,070
Wanxue,

942
00:43:27,550 --> 00:43:29,320
are you very fond of Xuanqing?

943
00:43:32,030 --> 00:43:33,230
But

944
00:43:33,360 --> 00:43:34,820
I don't know his feelings.

945
00:43:36,710 --> 00:43:37,970
Why would you say that?

946
00:43:39,360 --> 00:43:40,280
You don't know.

947
00:43:40,550 --> 00:43:41,510
After he returned to the capital,

948
00:43:41,510 --> 00:43:43,310
he has only been to my house once.

949
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:45,460
He only spoke to my father,

950
00:43:45,630 --> 00:43:46,360
and as for me,

951
00:43:46,630 --> 00:43:48,000
he spoke less than two sentences

952
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:48,930
before leaving.

953
00:43:54,150 --> 00:43:55,030
Wanxue,

954
00:43:57,880 --> 00:43:58,670
Third Aunt.

955
00:44:14,580 --> 00:44:17,900
[A Splendid Match]
